<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>You currently pay for your Kingsbridge business insurance policy&nbsp;<b><i>[policy number]</i></b>&nbsp;through direct debit payments.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Our credit providers Close Brothers Premium Finance have informed us that&nbsp;<b>your most recent direct debit payment failed on&nbsp;<i>[date]</i></b>.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><b><u>You do not need to do anything, as Close Brothers will re-attempt this payment on&nbsp;<i>[date]</i>.&nbsp;</u></b><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>If this second payment fails, our team will contact you directly to resolve.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><font face="arial"><i>If you have made a payment in the past 3 working days please disregard this email.</i></font><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><font face="arial">Kind regards,<br></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
